---
layout: layouts/base.vto
title: Playbooks
url: /docs/playbooks/
---
<article class="home">
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">Sigma · Playbooks</div>
    <h1>The<br><em>playbooks.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">How we review and operate, by discipline — the posture, the severity-ordered rubric, and the specific checks we run. Each pairs with an LLM-ready prompt in Prompts.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="section-block">
    <ul class="entry-list">
      {{ for entry of search.pages("section=playbooks", "title") }}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ entry.url }}">
          <span class="entry-title">{{ entry.title }}</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      {{ /for }}
    </ul>
  </div>
</article>
